T1  - Note—The Distribution Problem with Upper and Lower Bounds on the Node Requirements
AU  - Charnes, A.
AU  - Klingman, Darwin
Y1  - 1970/05/01
PY  - 1970
DA  - 1970/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.16.9.638
